{
  "id": "69d0e7443d1cb2cf6e60fab8",
  "title": "割合を取り合う競技の成果指標",
  "created": 1775298375,
  "updated": 1775302122,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d0e7443d1cb2cf6e60fab8",
      "text": "割合を取り合う競技の成果指標",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775298375,
      "updated": 1775298375
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0e7460000000000435918",
      "text": "割合を取り合う競技の成績はいずれ頭打ちになる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775298375,
      "updated": 1775298387
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0e753000000000043591a",
      "text": "\t例えば鯖江のメガネの国内シェアが 96% だろうと 97% だろうと大した違いを感じない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775298388,
      "updated": 1775298881
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0e941000000000043591b",
      "text": "\t100% に近い数値で1%を取る苦労を知っていると大した違いを感じられる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775298881,
      "updated": 1775298993
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0e74f0000000000435919",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775298383,
      "updated": 1775298383
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0e9b3000000000043591c",
      "text": "イレブンナイン",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775298996,
      "updated": 1775299329
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0eb850000000000435921",
      "text": " https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/イレブンナイン",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775299462,
      "updated": 1775299463
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0eb00000000000043591e",
      "text": "\t99.999999999% の純度を誇る物質",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775299329,
      "updated": 1775299360
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0eb40000000000043591f",
      "text": "\t\tケイ素をこの純度にして半導体材料にする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775299393,
      "updated": 1775299907
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0eb7e0000000000435920",
      "text": "\t鉄を99.9999% （シックスナイン）程度に純度を高めると錆びにくくなる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775299454,
      "updated": 1775299509
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0e9b3000000000043591d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775298996,
      "updated": 1775298996
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0edc70000000000435925",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300040,
      "updated": 1775300040
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0ed8c0000000000435923",
      "text": "賭け事でオッズが用いられることがよくあるが、どうよ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775299981,
      "updated": 1775300052
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0edd50000000000435926",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/80e01f8efd9b4bb14a30d43f565ba8b7]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300053,
      "updated": 1775300138
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0ee2a0000000000435927",
      "text": "\t小さい方は変化が小さくなって分かりづらいし大きい方は変化が大げさ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300138,
      "updated": 1775300200
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0ee970000000000435928",
      "text": "対数オッズ（ロジット）はどうよ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300248,
      "updated": 1775300260
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0eea30000000000435929",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/6792f36f0a3c054390ffbe55ea72fc7d]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300260,
      "updated": 1775301181
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0eea5000000000043592a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300261,
      "updated": 1775300261
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0ef10000000000043592c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300369,
      "updated": 1775300369
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f2440000000000435939",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775301188,
      "updated": 1775301188
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0ef04000000000043592b",
      "text": "小さい割合での競争は割とすぐに抜けるし、オッズのほうが良いかもしれない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300357,
      "updated": 1775300385
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0ef20000000000043592d",
      "text": "\t30点を60点にするのは簡単だが、60点を90点にするのは難しい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300385,
      "updated": 1775300411
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0ef79000000000043592e",
      "text": "\t賭け事でオッズが使われるのは何らかの視点でのわかりやすさがあるからだと思うが何だろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300474,
      "updated": 1775300501
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0efc8000000000043592f",
      "text": "\t\t同じ用語を違う意味で使ってるかもしれん",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300552,
      "updated": 1775300566
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f0130000000000435930",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300627,
      "updated": 1775300627
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f247000000000043593a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775301191,
      "updated": 1775301191
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f0130000000000435931",
      "text": "Wiikipedia のオッズにデカい数字が載っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300627,
      "updated": 1775300656
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f02f0000000000435932",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/90b3db575db5b69acf4f54e6dcdd1812]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300656,
      "updated": 1775300661
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f0340000000000435933",
      "text": "\t確率に直そう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300661,
      "updated": 1775300679
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f0470000000000435934",
      "text": " 競馬のオッズは直感的だがオッズの説明から想起される数字と逆",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775300680,
      "updated": 1775302009
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f2a7000000000043593b",
      "text": "\t[$ \\frac{p}{1-p}]じゃなくて[$ \\frac{1-p}{p}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775301288,
      "updated": 1775302024
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f320000000000043593e",
      "text": "\t\tというか賭け事のオッズはこちらだろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775301408,
      "updated": 1775301423
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f4a30000000000435943",
      "text": "\t\t逆関数は[$ p=\\frac1{1+x}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775301796,
      "updated": 1775301815
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f32e000000000043593f",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/ec4623090fa838f0053e7235e819e21a]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775301423,
      "updated": 1775301705
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f4490000000000435940",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/79e258359077c47b42dff9e19d71f54c]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775301705,
      "updated": 1775301726
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f45d0000000000435941",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/b83088a0fcf42eddfec6f98d18f43f83]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775301726,
      "updated": 1775301742
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f5120000000000435944",
      "text": " 最下位争いが凄い事になっている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775301906,
      "updated": 1775302068
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f5b40000000000435945",
      "text": " \t[単勝ロマン]（ギャンカスになりそうな発想）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775302069,
      "updated": 1775302122
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0f46d0000000000435942",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775301742,
      "updated": 1775301742
    },
    {
